&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;By bringing together next-gen technology and the finest live data available, Genius Sports is enabling a new era of sports for fans worldwide, delivering experiences that are more immersive, interactive and personalized than ever before. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.geniussports.com/about-us/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Learn more at geniussports.com&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;looking for a Senior Software Engineer on our Sports AI team to help build the next generation of real-time AI systems powering sports analysis and insights.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;These systems transform live sports broadcasts (incorporating signals from video, crowd noise, audio commentary, and text) into a structured understanding of game context and auto-generated insights. The outputs from these systems power a range of products including automated highlight clipping, augmented broadcasts, semi-automatic play-by-play collection, and natural-language insight generation.&amp;nbsp;For example, these systems can detect a goal, attribute it to the correct player, and localize where it occurred on the pitch within seconds by combining crowd noise spikes, commentary signals, and video cues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role sits at the intersection of streaming and distributed systems, AI, and product engineering.&amp;nbsp;You’ll&amp;nbsp;build and&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;real-time pipelines that process noisy, asynchronous inputs under tight latency constraints.&amp;nbsp;These systems combine traditional streaming and data processing techniques with modern&amp;nbsp;multimodal&amp;nbsp;AI models to produce reliable outputs in production.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You’ll&amp;nbsp;work on challenges like aligning signals across multiple sources, handling&amp;nbsp;uncertainty&amp;nbsp;and inconsistency in model outputs, and designing systems that degrade gracefully in real-world conditions. We are early in building these capabilities, so the role involves working through ambiguity, experimenting with different approaches, and building new systems from first principles where established patterns&amp;nbsp;don’t&amp;nbsp;yet exist.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;By bringing together next-gen technology and the finest live data available, Genius Sports is enabling a new era of sports for fans worldwide, delivering experiences that are more immersive, interactive and personalised than ever before.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; Learn more at &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.geniussports.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;geniussports.com.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;156&quot; data-end=&quot;496&quot;&gt;As an &lt;strong data-start=&quot;162&quot; data-end=&quot;194&quot;&gt;Automation Platform Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;ll build the platforms, integrations and AI-powered automation that help Genius Sports work smarter every day. From cloud infrastructure and identity platforms to business systems and internal tooling, you&#39;ll create solutions that simplify complex processes and have an impact across the company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;498&quot; data-end=&quot;1022&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on engineering role with a strong focus on automation and systems integration. You&#39;ll play a key role in developing an AI-powered automation platform that transforms how support requests are received, classified and routed, while collaborating with teams across the whole business to deliver scalable, reliable solutions. If you enjoy solving operational challenges, building from the ground up and taking ownership of your work, you&#39;ll thrive in this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;9i15tv&quot; data-start=&quot;1043&quot; data-end=&quot;1189&quot;&gt;Design, build and operate internal platforms, cloud-native applications and automation that improve operational efficiency across Genius Sports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s7fhv7&quot; data-start=&quot;1190&quot; data-end=&quot;1330&quot;&gt;Develop scalable APIs and integrations that connect identity platforms, business applications, collaboration tools and enterprise systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1rdx1vn&quot; data-start=&quot;1331&quot; data-end=&quot;1463&quot;&gt;Build and continuously improve AI-powered workflows that automate support processes, business operations and employee experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1n86kkl&quot; data-start=&quot;1464&quot; data-end=&quot;1595&quot;&gt;Design and maintain cloud infrastructure using Infrastructure as Code, while supporting CI/CD pipelines and platform reliability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;7v14jy&quot; data-start=&quot;1596&quot; data-end=&quot;1721&quot;&gt;Partner with Security, Identity, DevOps and Business Systems teams to deliver secure, scalable and well-governed solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;11noe3c&quot; data-start=&quot;1722&quot; data-end=&quot;1862&quot;&gt;Help shape engineering standards, contribute to technical documentation and review solutions delivered by external development partners to ensure quality and scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BRING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1yucm79&quot; data-start=&quot;308&quot; data-end=&quot;432&quot;&gt;Strong software engineering experience with Python, building production-quality applications and automation solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;wjxj2r&quot; data-start=&quot;433&quot; data-end=&quot;502&quot;&gt;Experience designing, deploying and operating solutions in AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;14n13na&quot; data-start=&quot;503&quot; data-end=&quot;623&quot;&gt;Experience building integrations using REST APIs, webhooks and authentication protocols such as OAuth2, SAML and SCIM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&qu

