&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Lead the end-to-end delivery of M&amp;amp;A integration&amp;nbsp;programmes, ensuring successful execution against agreed&amp;nbsp;objectives,&amp;nbsp;timelines&amp;nbsp;and value creation targets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:450,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
