&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Establish and manage&amp;nbsp;programme&amp;nbsp;governance, including&amp;nbsp;SteerCo&amp;nbsp;reporting, executive updates, decision&amp;nbsp;logs&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;programme&amp;nbsp;controls.&lt;/span&gt;&lt

