&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;By bringing together next-gen technology and the finest live data available, Genius Sports is enabling a new era of sports for fans worldwide, delivering experiences that are more immersive, interactive and personalised than ever before.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; Learn more at &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.geniussports.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;geniussports.com &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Junior HR Administrator, you’ll support the full employee journey - from onboarding new Geniuses to keeping our HR processes running smoothly. You’ll collaborate across teams, maintain accurate records, and handle sensitive information with care and confidentiality. If you’re organized, people-driven, and excited to learn and grow in HR, this role is the perfect start to your journey!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;419&quot;&gt;Supports HR operations and compliance: Assists with transitioning HR processes to Shared Services, ensuring accuracy, efficiency, and alignment with Bulgarian legal requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;419&quot;&gt;Prepares HR documentation: Creates and maintains employment contracts, letters, and other HR-related documents, ensuring legal compliance and timely delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;419&quot;&gt;Drives a smooth employee journey: Coordinates onboarding and offboarding activities, working closely with Talent Acquisition, Payroll, and Operations to deliver a seamless experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;419&quot;&gt;Maintains accurate records and benefits: Updates employee files and manages benefits such as food, transport, and multisport, ensuring timely activation and transparent communication with vendors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;419&quot;&gt;Upholds confidentiality and collaboration: Handles employee information with discretion, communicates openly with managers and stakeholders, and supports ethical, transparent HR practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IT WILL BE A BONUS IF YOU KNOW:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;120&quot; data-end=&quot;328&quot;&gt;Employee-focused and service-oriented: Provides a customer-first, employee-centric experience through timely, professional, and empathetic support and collaboration across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;120&quot; data-end=&quot;328&quot;&gt;Detail-driven and technically proficient: Skilled in Excel, Word, and SharePoint with strong attention to detail. Ensures data accuracy, identifies and corrects inconsistencies, and supports continuous process improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;120&quot; data-end=&quot;328&quot;&gt;Organized, transparent, and collaborative: Manages multiple priorities effectively while maintaining clear communication, accountability, and teamwork within the global People Team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We enjoy an ‘office-first’ culture and maximize opportunities to collaborate, connect and learn together. Our hybrid working models differ depending on your role and location.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;As well as a competitive salary and range of benefits, we’re committed to supporting employee wellbeing and helping you grow your skills, experience and career. Learn more about how rewarding life at Genius can be at&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.geniussports.com/reward/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt; Reward | Genius Sports.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
