&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;456&quot; data-end=&quot;467&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;469&quot; data-end=&quot;714&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a Match Lead to support live football and basketball operations. In this role, you’ll help run live games using Genius Sports technology, making sure tracking and event data is accurate and delivered on time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;716&quot; data-end=&quot;855&quot;&gt;You’ll lead Operators during live shifts, stay focused during game play, and give clear feedback to help improve our systems and processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;857&quot; data-end=&quot;880&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1379&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;946&quot;&gt;Lead a group of Operators across 1–2 football games per shift.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;947&quot; data-end=&quot;1040&quot;&gt;Track and confirm key game events, including dead balls, stoppage time and similar moments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1041&quot; data-end=&quot;1120&quot;&gt;Confirm teams, line-ups, players and player markings before and during games.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1121&quot; data-end=&quot;1205&quot;&gt;Stay focused during live ball situations and support accurate event data delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1206&quot; data-end=&quot;1296&quot;&gt;Join post-game meetings and share clear feedback with Operators and Operations Managers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1297&quot; data-end=&quot;1379&quot;&gt;Complete marking tasks that help improve the accuracy and design of our systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
