&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;By bringing together next-gen technology and the finest live data available, Genius Sports is enabling a new era of sports for fans worldwide, delivering experiences that are more immersive, interactive and personalised than ever before.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; Learn more at &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.geniussports.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;geniussports.com &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is also eligible for hybrid working (1-2days in the office).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE &amp;amp; TEAM&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will bridge the gap between our Finance and People teams to ensure that our Colombia payroll is processed seamlessly. We are looking for someone who has a drive for change and optimising our current processes as well as a natural tendency to be in the detail.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working within the Finance Team reporting into the Head of Transactional Processing, this role will work closely with the People Operations Team providing our Colombia payroll service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational delivery excellence:&amp;nbsp; &lt;/strong&gt;Responsible for the end-to-end operational delivery of the payroll including the employee experience with the monthly requirement of 100% accuracy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payroll and Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; Day to day responsibility for the successful processing of payroll and benefits enrolment, working with our payroll and benefits providers and finance colleagues on the delivery of these monthly processes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People Processes and Controls&lt;/strong&gt;: Ensuring compliance with internal policies, external regulations and that our SOX controls are met. Working with key stakeholders (e.g., people operations, the wider people team, systems and data team) to develop new ways of working that may be more effective and appropriate to our size.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data, Systems &amp;amp; Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt; Taking ownership of people data integrity within the payroll platform ensuring that it is aligned with Workday, that data accurate and regularly updated.&amp;nbsp; Support and promote effective use of Workday and other HR systems which impact and improve successful payroll delivery and accuracy.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Projects &amp;amp; Programmes:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the Finance team lead on payroll for projects relating to payroll governance, benefits renewals and implementation of any new people/benefits/payroll technology.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication &amp;amp; Ownership: &lt;/strong&gt;Point of contact for business relationship with external providers for payroll’s managed, owning regular communication and process improvements with 3rd parties.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DUTIES &amp;amp; RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage all aspects of payroll within Colombia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reviewing processed payroll for corrections;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with legislation and reporting requirements;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle holiday, absence, PILON and sick pay calculations where required;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overseeing tax-related payroll returns;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participating in system improvements;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with our tax team to run and manage year-end procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining internal controls and audit compliance;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Man

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;By bringing together next-gen technology and the finest live data available, Genius Sports is enabling a new&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;era of sports for fans worldwide, delivering experiences that are more immersive,&amp;nbsp;interactive&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;personalised&amp;nbsp;than ever before. Learn more at&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.geniussports.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Hyperlink&quot;&gt;geniussports.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:257}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
